{"tid":1658810,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［文宣入］建議整人種文宣","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:33:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T18:03:23.000Z","uid":15587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ca5a2081a0e7bed09de4dd55407719764c1958c2","tid":1658810,"uid":15587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:33:52.000Z","msg":"利用文宣 將香港人嘅精神宣揚出去<br />\n俾全世界睇到 我地香港人不論膚色 <br />\n係東方文化大熔爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff77a7a0f0d9c8b7899b7fd8190b0f03f6229ed","tid":1658810,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人可唔可以爭爭氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日美國眾議院通過香港民主人權法案<br />\n你當撚人condom咩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n通過左就唔駛多謝人？<br />\n仲有呀！<br />\n條Bill 未過參議院架！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好咁老定！<br />\n唔該去twitter多謝人地支持，<br />\n然後講香港真係好需要條Bill啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#hongkonghumanrightsanddemocracyact <br />\n#standwithhongkong<br />\n#fightforfreedom<br />\n<br />\n留意番Representatives 同Senator係有分別，<br />\n望清楚其他人點叫人先好！<br />\n唔好叫人First Name！<br />\n<br />\ntwitter 組已經將議員的tweets<br />\n放左入bot task1<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=Wg3pkMW64ksxbb%2FAt9Sry7PGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=e27b0dbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入<span style=\"color: violet;\"> /task1</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWmYt8Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWmYt8Z.png&h=b245ba88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ntask1所顯示的25條tweets<br />\n係嚴重唔夠人<br />\n（大佬呀條條上唔到一千點搞呀？）<br />\n<br />\n最後咪撚再串錯hongkong!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b33c53281a2f12c665bc6f25cf2954e9fa72bf4","tid":1658810,"uid":15587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:36:32.000Z","msg":"香港人所追求嘅民主 黑人 白人 黃種人 棕色人種都曾經追求過 有人成功 有人失敗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471390bf97b05b8917cceeb59886aeacbd9507be","tid":1658810,"uid":15587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e113ba8b2cf6d888e596b51be3af10336f9f1d39","tid":1658810,"uid":15587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:37:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0523c13005f184364f4028170b9e1a9bba82ec9d","tid":1658810,"uid":15587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"幫手推下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d89c81e2f9b95817eff5a426b8359e084e676a0","tid":1658810,"uid":303799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit